These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: fantasy, time-travel, documentary, spy, family, action, satire
There are 7 different favourite colors: yellow, mauve, grey, blood-red, ebony, lavender, pink
 1. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is not the person who likes lavender##6
 3. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 4. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ebony##5
 5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 6. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person watching action movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who likes mauve##7
 8. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person who likes grey##7
10. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
11. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
12. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes pink##5
13. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
14. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
15. the person watching family movies is the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Movie-Genre          | documentary    | fantasy    | time-travel | action | spy | family    | satire |
| Color   | ebony | yellow | grey  | lavender   | blood-red    | mauve | pink |

