.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, davidoff, dannemann, aristoff, vegafina, alhambra, cain
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, balloon-flower, daisy, dahlia, rose, daffodil
 1. the person who growsrose is somewhere between the cain-smoker and the davidoff-smoker##7
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is the aristoff-smoker##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 5. the bongani-smoker is somewhere between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growsiris##7
 6. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere between the aristoff-smoker and the person who growsballoon-flower##7
 7. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere between the aristoff-smoker and the davidoff-smoker##7
 8. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the left of the vegafina-smoker##5
10. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
11. the person who growsrose is not the cain-smoker##6
12. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
13. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who growsdaisy and the aristoff-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Cigar    | cain  | dannemann | alhambra | aristoff | bongani     | vegafina | davidoff  |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | rose | iris  | daffodil  | dahlia | daisy      | marigold |

