.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: orange, red, ivory, pink, lilac, emerald, aquamarine
There 7 different types of food: cauliflower, cabbage, plum, eggplant, onion, peach, cucumber
 1. the person eating cucumber is between the person who likes ivory and the person eating plum##2
 2. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
 3. the person eating cabbage is not the person who likes pink##6
 4. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
 5. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating peach and the person who likes lilac##2
 6. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person who likes pink##5
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
 9. the person who likes ivory is somewhere between the person eating onion and the person eating cucumber##7
10. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
11. the person who likes lilac is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes lilac is not the person eating cauliflower##6
13. the person who likes emerald is somewhere between the person who likes red and the person who likes lilac##7
14. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
15. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
16. the person who likes lilac is not the person eating peach##6
17. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
18. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
19. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating onion##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
| Color         | orange | red | emerald | lilac  | ivory | pink | aquamarine |
| Food   | cabbage   | peach       | cauliflower   | onion | eggplant           | cucumber     | plum     |

