.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-4::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  dressmaker, electrician, engineer, paramedic, bartender, scientist, photographer
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: martial-arts, superhero, scientific, sports, satire, spy, action
 1. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
 2. the engineer is in an odd position##4
 3. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
 4. the bartender is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
 5. the paramedic is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
 6. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching satire movies##7
 8. the paramedic is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
10. the scientist is in an even position##4
11. the scientist is somewhere between the bartender and the electrician##7
12. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
13. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
14. the engineer is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
15. the photographer is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
16. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
17. the person watching sports movies is between the scientist and the person watching spy movies##2
18. the bartender is not the person watching action movies##6
19. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2    |     3     |     4      |     5      |    6    |    7     |
| Job       | paramedic | dressmaker    | engineer   | photographer | bartender     | scientist  | electrician |
| Movie-Genre   | satire    | scientific | superhero | spy      | sports | martial-arts | action      |

