.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skiing, swimming, badminton, lacrosse, snowboarding, climbing, volleyball
There are 7 different nationalities: polish, american, australian, colombian, mexican, spanish, japanese
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 2. the spanish is somewhere between the polish and the australian##7
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
 4. the colombian is not the person who's sport is climbing##6
 5. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
 8. the polish is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
 9. the spanish is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
10. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
12. the person who's sport is badminton is the mexican##1
13. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
14. the person who's sport is swimming is the american##1
15. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
16. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
