There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, iced-tea, water, cola, mirinda, sprite
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 8. the person drinking juice is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
10. the person drinking water is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
11. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
13. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person drinking water##1
15. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
17. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3

.:: Answer ::.
