 8. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
 9. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
10. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is surfing is the owner of the mouse##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
