14. the person who's sport is skiing is not the owner of the turtle##6
15. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the hamster##7
16. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
17. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the goat##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Pet           | hamster | turtle | fish   | goat | bird | goldfish | mouse |
| Sport   | parkour     | tennis       | water-polo | badminton       | skiing   | skateboarding | surfing  |

